{"id":571415,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/【立此存照】写歌寻衅滋事《一人一票》-创作/","date":"2017-11-04T06:21:28Z","modified":"2017-11-04T07:51:59Z","title":"【立此存照】写歌“寻衅滋事”《一人一票》 创作者被捕","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>据刘晓原律师在推特透露，广东居民徐琳疑因创作歌曲《一人一票》而被当局以“寻衅滋事”罪逮捕。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-lang=\"en\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"zh\">罕见的案例：这些年来，见过很多离奇的寻衅滋事案。但因为“创作歌曲”而被以涉嫌寻衅滋事罪逮捕，这还是第一例。 <a href=\"https://t.co/A7zcQJSn8W\">pic.twitter.com/A7zcQJSn8W</a></p>\n<p>— 刘晓原律师 (@liu_xiaoyuan) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/liu_xiaoyuan/status/926305237408792581?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 3, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/DNrlrFmUQAAXrg7.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-571417\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/DNrlrFmUQAAXrg7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/DNrlrFmUQAAXrg7.jpg 729w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/DNrlrFmUQAAXrg7-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>逮捕通知书</strong></p>\n<p>经广州市南沙区人民检察院批准，我局于2017年11月02日15时对涉嫌寻衅滋事罪的徐琳执行逮捕，现羁押在广州市南沙区看守所。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">广东省广州市公安局南沙区分局<br />\n二〇一七年十一月二日</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>附歌曲</strong>：徐琳《一人一票》</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/xUgitLBMx4c?rel=0\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,27949],"tags":[25968,18820,23705,9212]}